# {{SERVICE_NAME}} - Memobase AI Memory

Self-hosted AI memory service for persistent user profiles.

## Features

- User memory persistence for AI applications
- LLM-based memory summarization
- PostgreSQL backend storage
- Redis caching

## Environment Variables

Required (set in .env.secrets):
- `OPENAI_API_KEY` - OpenAI API key for LLM operations

## Usage

```python
from memobase import MemobaseClient

client = MemobaseClient(
    project_url="http://localhost:{{SERVICE_PORT}}",
    api_key="your-api-key"
)
```

